      <title>Altice France 将 XpFibre 股份从债权人手中转移出去</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/altice-france-shifts-xpfibre-stake-out-of-creditors-reach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice France 表示，其将 XpFibre 股份捐赠给一家控股公司，该公司在偿还股东贷款后不受某些债务契约的约束。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/altice-france-shifts-xpfibre-stake-out-of-creditors-reach</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 15:24:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟探讨 Telegram 是否受严格的新内容法约束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/eu-explores-whether-telegram-falls-under-strict-new-content-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telegram 是一个被俄罗斯虚假信息传播者利用的消息平台，欧盟对用于传播非法和有害内容的在线平台进行打击，该平台面临着受到打击的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/eu-explores-whether-telegram-falls-under-strict-new-content-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:55:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 支持的运动员权利初创公司筹集了 4000 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/athlete-rights-startup-backed-by-bill-ackman-raises-40-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由诺瓦克·德约科维奇 (Novak Djokovic) 共同创立的职业网球运动员协会 (Professional Tennis Players Association) 的营利性机构获胜者联盟 (Winners Alliance) 已从亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 的潘兴广场基金会 (Pershing Square Foundation) 和 Prysm Capital 等现有投资者那里又筹集了 4000 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/athlete-rights-startup-backed-by-bill-ackman-raises-40-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 14:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃利奥特 (Elliott) 目标是德州仪器 (TI) 现金流达 25 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/activist-elliott-takes-2-5-billion-texas-instruments-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[激进投资者埃利奥特投资管理公司 (Elliott Investment Management) 已向德州仪器 (TI) 投资了超过 25 亿美元，并正在推动这家芯片制造商改善其自由现金流。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/activist-elliott-takes-2-5-billion-texas-instruments-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:45:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice International 搁置出售多米尼加资产的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/altice-international-shelves-plans-to-sell-dominican-assets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice International 已搁置出售多米尼加共和国资产的计划，因为该公司仍在探索削减债务的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/altice-international-shelves-plans-to-sell-dominican-assets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 13:32:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比亚迪展示可实现超长行驶的新型混合动力系统</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/byd-shows-off-new-hybrid-powertrain-capable-of-ultra-long-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比亚迪公司推出了一种新型混合动力系统，能够让汽车在不充电或加油的情况下行驶超过 2,000 公里（1,250 英里）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/byd-shows-off-new-hybrid-powertrain-capable-of-ultra-long-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 12:56:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电子游戏零售商 GameStop 融资近 10 亿美元，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/gamestop-shares-rally-as-video-game-retailer-raises-nearly-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[GameStop Corp. 股价周二延续涨势，此前这家视频游戏零售商表示，由于人们对所谓的 meme 股票重新产生了兴趣，该公司通过股票出售计划获得了近 10 亿美元的收入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/gamestop-shares-rally-as-video-game-retailer-raises-nearly-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>T-Mobile 将以约 24 亿美元收购美国移动资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/t-mobile-to-buy-us-cellular-assets-in-roughly-2-4-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国第二大移动运营商 T-Mobile US Inc. 已同意以约 24 亿美元收购 US Cellular Corp. 的无线业务及其部分频谱资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/t-mobile-to-buy-us-cellular-assets-in-roughly-2-4-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 11:37:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OpenAI 在解散安全团队后成立了由 Sam Altman 担任监督委员会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/openai-forms-board-safety-committee-after-criticism-ilya-sutskever-departure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OpenAI 成立了一个董事会委员会来评估其人工智能模型的安全性和安保性，这是在该主题的最高管理人员辞职并且公司实际上解散了其内部团队几周后进行的治理变革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-28/openai-forms-board-safety-committee-after-criticism-ilya-sutskever-departure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 May 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
